entries.waypoint_description_1: A cave where it's rumored a Krayt Dragon lives... well, as of 80 years ago, that is.
entries.player_sorry: Not yet. I am still looking.
entries.player_reset: I have decided to quit looking.
entries.player_3_1: Where do you plan to find a Krayt Dragon?
entries.player_1_1: I'd love to see a Krayt Dragon!
entries.npc_reset: You're just scared, that's all. Me and my friends aren't scared... well, not that much.
entries.npc_4_1: We've been told stories all about it. My grandpa said he knew where one used to live. He said he found the Dragon in the cave and punched it in the nose. My grandpa's a good guy and he wouldn't lie, no-siree!
entries.npc_3_1: You're just scared, that's all. Me and my friends aren't scared... well, not that much.
entries.npc_2_1: Yeah, me too! I don't think they're as scary as they're made out to be. This is where my grandpa told me where he saw one when he was a kid! Good luck!
entries.npc_1_1: Have you ever heard of the story that young Sand People boys prove their age of ascension by going out and touching the nose of a Krayt Dragon? Me and my friends know where to find one and are going to do it tomorrow. You wanna go too?
